Fantastic stay at this elegant resort with picturesque views & attentive staff *****
We enjoyed a fantastic stay at this sprawling and well-maintained idyllic resort for our first visit to Danang, Vietnam. From the moment we were warmly greeted at the airport, to the Villa on the Rocks with its infinity pool & picturesque ocean views, top-rated local fusion and French cuisine at Citron and La Maison 1888 restaurants, and of course their friendly and knowledgeable staff who are always courteous and helpful to assist with our various activities & dining reservations -- we thoroughly relished this romantic getaway/journey of healing at Son Tra Peninsula. High praise to our private villa host Randy for his attentive & efficient service, restaurant staff Harry & Tan (plus the diligent gentleman on 'monkey patrol' around Nonla outdoor tables area:), Hong the…
