Da Nang Intercontinental hotel 5 star bliss
This is my second time in one year to visit the Intercontinental in da Nang Vietnam. It is an exceptional property, and I would be happy to come again, and encourage others to do the same. The service and the smiles are everywhere, and they are very attentive and quite helpful and courteous. The food was quite good and the room is exquisite and details are not overlooked. I look forward to coming back again and sharing my. recommendation with others.
