Must visit!
The architecture of the hotel is breathtaking! Everything is beautifully crafted, and the cable car was so fun! Love the theme of diving different levels of the hotel in different element. Citron was so yummy, everything was fresh, staff was beyond friendly. We were there for my mom's birthday, they gave her a surprise birthday cake, everything was so thoughtful. Definitely recommend and would love to visit again if I come to Da Nang again!
