Shawn X wrote a review Feb 2024
San Francisco, California2 contributions
Can't wait for our next visit
We had an amazing stay in the resort, spending 2 nights in one of the magnificent villas. We had the pleasure of having Krystal as our host, who took great care of us, satisfying all of our asks, big and small. Our stay in the resort can't be the same level without her standing by 24x7. The villa is totally worth the extra price, with lounge access (exclusive breakfast, afternoon tea, cocktail hours), special perks, private pools, etc. We've already decided to come back next year as a bigger family in summer, when Krystal mentioned we'll have chance to snorkel right on resort's beaches.
